T02D2413:33a-1: tsa bu ra mukti ka ra tsa au p'a ya n'a ma /
T02D2413:33a-3: 'jigs pa brgyad rmongs par byed pa'i thabs zhes bya ba /
T02D2413:33a-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2413:33a-5: sprul stag chom rkun mda' dang me yi ni //
T02D2413:33a-6: 'jigs pas mi 'jigs klu sgrub gdams pa thob //
T02D2413:33a-7: skar mkhan bi kha na ni 'jigs med de //
T02D2413:33a-8: 'on kyang rnal 'byor nyams kyi nus pa bri //
T02D2413:33a-9: sems nyid 'dul zhing bdud 'joms rnal 'byor la //
T02D2413:33a-10: las ni ma rtogs rkyen gyi bar chod 'byung //
T02D2413:33a-11: de phyir dang po'i rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos //
T02D2413:33a-12: 'jigs skyob dran zhing bla ma spyi bor bsgom //
T02D2413:33a-13: sbyor ba byas pa'i snying bo la sogs bzla //
T02D2413:33a-14: aom ste aa rjes la ni bzhi pas sbyar //
T02D2413:33a-15: ka phreng gnyis pa las byung gsum pa ste //
T02D2413:33a-16: aa phreng gsum pa rnal 'byor 'brel par mdzod //
T02D2413:33a-17: bam gyis bcings te dha ni rjes su bri //
T02D2413:33a-18: rkan gyi dang po dbyangs can lnga pas bcings //
T02D2413:33a-19: la dang ai 'byor sha za'i skad yin no //
T02D2413:33b-0: dbyangs can bcu gsum yi ge tsa @33b yig ni //
T02D2413:33b-1: 'brel nas mthar yang 'byung chen gnyis pa bri //
T02D2413:33b-2: phyis 'byung seng ge'i nang du stag ltar spyod //
T02D2413:33b-3: bhy'a ghra'i sgra sgrogs stag gi 'jigs pa mang //
T02D2413:33b-4: ka na dh'a bzla zhing mda' yi 'jigs pa bral //
T02D2413:33b-5: sa ba pa snal chen rnams kyi 'jigs pa sel //
T02D2413:33b-6: mu ham kha bcings bandha sv'a h'a bri//
T02D2413:33b-7: 'gro ba'i don du rnal 'byor sems bskyed nas //
T02D2413:33b-8: bzlas bya nyon mongs bral zhing thar pa thob //
T02D2413:33b-9: aa khu nag po'i khrag gis mig sman dang //
T02D2413:33b-10: sor bzhi'i shing bu blangs nas rnam par 'phyang //
T02D2413:33b-11: zla brgyad ngo yi yan lag brgyad blangs nas //
T02D2413:33b-12: zla ba'i zhag la mchod dang gtor ma bya //
T02D2413:33b-13: zla zin dus su mi snang sgrub bzlas bya //
T02D2413:33b-14: tshe na'i sbyor bas mgo ni mthong min no //
T02D2413:33b-15: mi mthong mi snang sbyor ba 'di yin no //
T02D2413:33b-16: aom ka li ka li ma h'a ka li /
T02D2413:33b-19: sma sha na bha si ni dha byi dang /
T02D2413:33b-20: ma mam pa shyantu ma nu sha //
T02D2413:33b-21: aa dang ha ha hr'i h'um sv'a h'a mthar //
T02D2413:33b-22: brgyad dang bcu bzhi nag po'i tshes la ni //
T02D2413:33b-23: gos dmar gcer bu dur khrod mtshan mo ni //
T02D2413:33b-24: khri bzlas rakta'i gtor mas mi snang 'grub //
T02D2413:33b-25: da ni rnal 'byor yang snying sbyor ba ni //
T02D2413:33b-26: snying po 'di lta ste gzhan yang zhal las blang //
T02D2413:33b-27: aom ru dhi ka r'a ti /
T02D2413:33b-31: kshu pa kshu pa sv'a h'a //
T02D2413:33b-32: 'di ni brgyad brgya rnal 'byor bzlas byas nas //
T02D2413:33b-33: lam du 'gro ba'i dus su sbyor ba bya //
T02D2413:33b-34: sprul stag tshom rkun mda' bcing bshang byas nas //
T02D2413:33b-35: sreg byed me yi nus pa'i rten 'brel bshad //
T02D2413:33b-36: chu sbal btang ba sbal tshil dza ma bhi ra chu //
T02D2413:33b-37: zhib tu btags nas rkang pa lag pa bsku //
T02D2413:33b-38: 'di ltar snying po nye snying bshad byas nas //
T02D2413:33b-39: shar ba'i mar gyis gtor nas sreg mi nus //
T02D2413:33b-40: siddhi n'a g'a rdzun pa dang ni //
T02D2413:33b-41: aa gni mo ha ra ti ra sgra dang //
T02D2413:33b-42: de rjes te ta dad ran te bri //
T02D2413:33b-43: ni pa ri bha na te me nus med //
T02D2413:33b-44: aom siddhi ni g'a rdzu na pa ste //
T02D2413:33b-45: pa yi ra gsum mthar sngags rdzogs par bzla //
T02D2413:33b-46: lan gsum gcod cing yungs kar mar khu gtor //
T02D2413:33b-47: lcags bsregs me ru zhugs kyang sreg mi nus //
T02D2413:33b-48: nus pa mthar phyin sngags sbyor gnyis pa ni //
T02D2413:33b-49: na mo la bhi shva mi tra ya te //
T02D2413:33b-50: h'u ta bha ha ha stam stam bha ya mi //
T02D2413:33b-51: tsi li sv'a h'a med nus med par gyis //
T02D2413:34a-2: rim bzhin bsgrubs na 'grub 'gyur the tshom med //
